  "2026-06-07T07:55:26.408Z",codex-5.3-full-cycle,"pm-web release:check passed after dependency alignment and generated frontend JS cleanup from git-tracked sources."
  "2026-06-07T08:00:45.580Z",codex-5.3-full-cycle,"Security gate: high-confidence token/key regex scan over tracked files and git history found no actionable secrets. Binary-history false positives were traced to embedded wasm base64 blobs, not credentials."
  "2026-06-12T11:53:16.482Z",codex-audit,"2026-06-12 package/release audit: release workflow contains unresolved merge-conflict markers and is invalid YAML. package.json is private:true but release.yml includes npm publish, so publish intent is contradictory. TypeScript-only compliance gap: public/src has tracked generated .js and .js.map alongside .ts sources. Dev/lock dependencies are staged to latest @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.6.12 and pm-changelog 2026.6.10. Files to review: .github/workflows/release.yml, package.json, package-lock.json, .gitignore, public/src/**/*.js, public/src/**/*.js.map."
